data.description: Nestled on almost half an acre in a cul-de-sac, this charming brick home has it all. This property features a beautiful main residence, detached 2 car garage with flex space above and a newer above ground saltwater pool with a wraparound deck! This four-bedroom, two-bathroom home has just completed numerous updates and is ready for its new owner. Upon entering the home, you are greeted with a large formal living room and dining room. Through the formal dining room, you enter the updated kitchen with stainless appliances and granite countertops. The kitchen is open to an eat-in breakfast nook and family room with beamed vaulted ceilings and brick fireplace. Off the kitchen is a large FROG, huge sunroom, and the large, converted garage that serves as the fourth bedroom  This home has multiple areas for entertaining both indoors and outside. Step outside to your personal oasis - a newer above-ground saltwater pool with a wraparound deck is perfect for relaxation and outdoor gatherings. The expansive yard is adorned with mature tropical plants, fruit trees and grape vines. A detached 2-car garage adds practicality and affords a wealth of opportunities. Situated in the serene Otranto neighborhood, this home provides tranquility while still being conveniently close to amenities, Hanahan schools, and parks. Please see the attached list of upgrades and amenities and floor plan in the documents section. 4th bedroom could be converted back to full attached 2 car garage if buyer desired.
